interpretation: The "woman cartwheeling" card represents agility, playfulness, and a sense of adventure. This card encourages you to approach life with a lighthearted and carefree attitude, finding joy in the journey rather than just focusing on the destination. It reminds you to stay flexible and adaptable, ready to pivot and change course when necessary. This card may also indicate a need for physical activity and movement, as well as a desire to try new things and take risks. Embrace your inner child and let yourself be spontaneous, open to the unexpected twists and turns that life may bring.
